						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone near the Vīrabhadra temple. </p>						

						<p>12th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This damaged and worn out inscription records the setting up of the hero-stone in memory of someone whose name is not clear.</p>						

						<p>The characters of the record belong to the 12th century A.D.</p>						

